name: Green - Hanging Sneaker Print
description:
Created as part of the series "Melbourne Sole"

Printed on high quality Photo stock. 

This sale is for a 10" x 15" Limited Edition print. 
I'll only be producing 100 prints of this photo.


SHIPPING DETAILS
I do my best to package everything so that nothing happens to your order in shipment. Sadly, I can't control what the post office does to the package once I hand it over to them. If a print is damaged during shipping, I will happily replace it under the condition that you ship the bent one back to me.

All prints are shipped through Australian Post encased between card, unless otherwise stated. If you would like insurance on you package please contact me and I will send you and updated invoice.

©2012 Logan Moody
All copyright and reproduction rights are retained by the artist.
